    <title>Hexo+Next搭建个人博客完整教程</title>
    <link href="https://lvshuncai.com/archives/4a17b156.html"/>
    <id>https://lvshuncai.com/archives/4a17b156.html</id>
    <published>2019-01-19T14:21:13.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-01-19T16:45:23.430Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Hexo+Next搭建个人博客完整教程，小白快速入门教程</p><a id="more"></a><h3 id="官方网站"><a href="#官方网站" class="headerlink" title="官方网站"></a>官方网站</h3><ul><li><a href="https://github.com/hexojs/hexo" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hexo</a></li><li><a href="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Next</a></li><li><a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hexo官网</a>  </li><li><a href="https://theme-next.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Next博客</a></li><li><a href="http://theme-next.iissnan.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Next文档</a></li></ul><h3 id="博客搭建"><a href="#博客搭建" class="headerlink" title="博客搭建"></a>博客搭建</h3><h4 id="安装前提"><a href="#安装前提" class="headerlink" title="安装前提"></a>安装前提</h4><ul><li><a href="https://imjad.cn/baidu/?q=Git%20%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Git 安装</a></li><li><a href="https://imjad.cn/baidu/?q=Nodejs%20%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Nodejs</a></li></ul><h4 id="安装Hexo"><a href="#安装Hexo" class="headerlink" title="安装Hexo"></a>安装Hexo</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="初始化博客"><a href="#初始化博客" class="headerlink" title="初始化博客"></a>初始化博客</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo init &lt;folder&gt;</span><br><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> &lt;folder&gt;</span><br><span class="line">$ npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="Hexo启动"><a href="#Hexo启动" class="headerlink" title="Hexo启动"></a>Hexo启动</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="浏览博客"><a href="#浏览博客" class="headerlink" title="浏览博客"></a>浏览博客</h4><p>访问 <a href="http://localhost:4000" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://localhost:4000</a></p><h4 id="Hexo部署到Github-Pages"><a href="#Hexo部署到Github-Pages" class="headerlink" title="Hexo部署到Github Pages"></a>Hexo部署到Github Pages</h4><ul><li>创建GitHub账号</li><li>创建仓库&lt;Github账号名称&gt;.github.io</li><li><p>修改站点配置文件_config.yml</p>  <figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">deploy:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">  type:</span> <span class="string">git</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">  repo:</span> <span class="attr">https://github.com/ShunCai/shuncai.github.io.git</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">  branch:</span> <span class="string">master</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">  name:</span> <span class="string">Licfe</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">  email:</span> <span class="string">lvshuncai@gmail.com</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>部署</p>  <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo cl &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>浏览博客：<a href="https://shuncai.github.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://shuncai.github.io/</a></p></li><li>自定义域名（可选）<ul><li>域名解析(表格二选一填写即可)</li></ul></li></ul><table><thead><tr><th>记录类型</th><th>主机记录</th><th>记录值</th><th>效果</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>CNAME</td><td>github</td><td>shuncai.github.io</td><td>访问 <a href="http://github.lvshuncai.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://github.lvshuncai.com</a> 等于访问 <a href="https://shuncai.github.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://shuncai.github.io/</a></td></tr><tr><td>CNAME</td><td>www</td><td>shuncai.github.io</td><td>访问 <a href="http://www.lvshuncai.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://www.lvshuncai.com</a> 等于访问 <a href="https://shuncai.github.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://shuncai.github.io/</a></td></tr></tbody></table><pre><code>- 仓库设置    - 打开仓库设置 https://github.com/ShunCai/shuncai.github.io/settings    - Custom domain 填写自定义域名    - 博客站点目录下添加CNAME文件，写入自定义域名</code></pre><h4 id="其它常用命令"><a href="#其它常用命令" class="headerlink" title="其它常用命令"></a>其它常用命令</h4><ul><li><p>Hexo清理</p>  <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo clear</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>Hexo生成</p>  <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>Hexo指定端口启动</p>  <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo server -p 5000</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>Hexo清理&amp;生成&amp;启动</p>  <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo cl &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>Hexo部署到远程站点</p>  <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo cl &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul>]]></content>
    
